transcript:

Hmm hmm.

Executive: Isi ke liye maine call kiya maine na aapko kafi dino pehle bhi connect kiya tha main daily basis pe aapko call kar rahi hoon but aapne bola tha baad mein call kijiyega baad mein.
Customer: Madam madam dekhiye madam ji madam ji humne pehle de first hi bola tha is baat ke liye ki jo humne yahan pe ek bar lock kar di usme koi bhi changes nahi hone chahiye.
Humne to bola ki mujhe NCR mein karna hai aap bina matlab ke idhar udhar pata nahi kahan kahan ki leads.
Executive: To usi ke solution ke liye to main aapko kafi time se call kar rahi hoon sir but aap mujhse ek bar bataiye aap connect hi nahi karenge.
Customer: Are ye hota hi kyun hai mujhe batao mera to kehna yahi hai main shuru se ye baat karta rehta hoon hamesha.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Ye hota hi kyun hai parivar aap log change karte kyun ho?
Executive: Change nahi karte hain abhi dekhiye aap keh rahe ho ki aapko ek example jaise south side ki aapko chahiye right aap ye keh rahe ho.
Customer: Main kyun chahiye south side kisne bola aapko south side chahiye matlab for example bol rahi hoon main matlab.
Customer: Nahi nahi nahi nahi nahi example bhi nahi sunna na mujhe mujhe Delhi ka chahiye mujhe NCR NCR ka chahiye.
Executive: Theek hai aapko NCR ka chahiye aap location ka issue hai na to usi ke liye main aapko batati hoon ki dekhiye agar aapne jaise preferred location aap chahte hain ki aapko isi location ki buyleads aaye abhi aisa to koi nahi hai ki aapko sirf usi location ki aayegi baki ki nahi aayegi baki ki bhi aayegi but ye hota hai ki agar aap jyada se jyada jis location ki aap chahte hain usi ki lead consume kare na to fir wo aapko usi consumption behavior pe aapko usi type ki lead aani start ho jayegi.
Customer: Madam madam meri baat suno sabse pehle madam meri baat suno.
Customer: Kam se kam saikdon ke sankhya mein to maine delete kar diya abhi main not relevant not relevant karta chala jata hoon theek hai fir bhi bar bar aap unhi chipkate rehte ho.
Customer: To ab ek baat batao kaise matlab kaise aadmi kare kam batao acha pichli bar yahi issue aaya tha bar bar hamara issue ye rehta hai hum isiliye service base kar rahe hain bar bar aapke sath mein humne bada package liya sab package liya lekin aap log kya karte ho yahan ke lead to hoti nahi hai Delhi ki ya Ghaziabad, Noida, Gurgaon theek hai hume is tarah ki lead chahiye aap log 90% lead utha ke udhar fekte ho pata nahi kya kya pata nahi kya kya likh ke aata rehta hai kuch samajh mein nahi aata.
Executive: Main aapka problem samajh rahi hoon dekhiye aapne invest kiya hai agar aapko business nahi milega to aap frustrate karoge to aapko genuine hai aapka irritate hona.
Customer: Madam dekho meri baat suno madam maine de first bola us time bhi kaha tha ki hum bar bar ye issue nahi chahte hain aapke team ne bhi mujhe assure kiya tha aap jo kar doge usko hum final kar denge iske baad hum koi change nahi karenge.
Customer: Fir ye kaise hota hai ki matlab 100 lead aa rahe hain to usme se 98 lead aapki bahar ki rehti hain south ki farzi farzi lead pata nahi kya matlab hai usme mobile number mobile number band.
Executive: To sabhi location ki aati hai hum aisa to nahi kar sakte sirf particular ki aaye wo sabhi ki aayegi lekin main aapko wahi bolne ki koshish kar rahi hoon main solution pe hi ja rahi hoon main aapko to aap please wahi suniye na isliye maine aapko discussion kiya aapki baat genuine hai main samajh gayi hoon.
Customer: Are madam ghanton mein ghanton mein IndiaMART mein ghanton mattha mar chuka hoon aap log karoge apne man ki theek hai.
Executive: Sir man ki nahi aap ek bar check kar lijiye aapka jo pehle account manage karte the abhi main new account manager hoon maine sari cheeze aapki check kari hai aapse baat ki hai.
Executive: To usi ke hisab se main karungi na aap ek bar mujh pe trust to karke dekhiye aapka last experience kharab raha hai aapne bata diya main samajh gayi hoon.

Hai na?
Executive: Haan ji main samajh rahi hoon sir iske liye.
Customer: Bas itni request hai madam bas.
Executive: Sir samajh rahi hoon usi ke solution ke liye main call kar rahi hoon aap ek bar mujh pe trust to kijiye jaise aap video meet ke liye kab available ho sakte hain mujhe bataiye aap ek bar trust karke video meet pe aaiyega uske baad agar jo hum cheeze batayenge discuss karenge changes karenge uske baad agar aapko fark sach mein dikhega aap ek bar trust to kar lijiye please.

Executive: Kal kal to nahi parso ke liye chalega?

Executive: Kis time available honge?
Customer: Subah 11 baje baat kar lijiye madam.

Hmm hmm.

Executive: Theek hai ek second aap line pe rahiyega 11:30.
Executive: Abhi possible nahi hai sir?

Executive: Theek hai ek second line pe rahiyega to abhi kar lete hain.

Executive: Theek hai line pe rahiyega.

Hmm hmm.
Executive: Abhi aap apna number bataiye whatsapp wala.
Customer: 8160.
Executive: 81 madam same number hai.
Customer: Same number hai.
Customer: 8160 8 same number se baat bhi wahi number hai madam same number hai.
Executive: Line pe rahiyega.
Hmm.

Executive: To main aapko na jo register email id hai usse hi aap join kar rahe ho?

Executive: Ek second just one minute five 15.
Executive: Abhi main aapko link share karungi whatsapp pe usko connect kijiyega aur jab main link share karungi na whatsapp pe uske na kuch reply kar dijiyega tabhi wo eligible hoga matlab join karne ke liye aapki side se theek hai.
Hmm hmm.
Executive: Main jab aapko message karungi join kar lijiye tab aap join kar lijiyega theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai aise kar lo.
Executive: Main share kar rahi hoon.
summary:
Concerns:

- Receiving leads from unwanted locations.

- Wants leads only from Delhi NCR region.

- Dissatisfied with lead quality and irrelevant leads.



Resolution:

- Executive acknowledged the customer's concerns.

- Agreed to schedule a video meet to discuss issues.

- Executive shared WhatsApp number to share meeting link.



Next Steps: 

- Video meet scheduled for the day after tomorrow.



Alert (If Any):

None

- Angry -> Neutral
